Detailed Description

The reply of an RouteExpandItemRequestPacket.

After the normal header this packet contains (subType = ROUTEEXPANDITEM_REPLY and 0 below is REPLY_HEADER_SIZE):
PosSizeComment {tabular}{lll} { Pos} & { Size} & { Description} \ $X$ & 4 bytes & User data \ $X+4$ & 4 bytes & Map id \ $X+8$ & 4 bytes & Nbr of items in result \ for each & 2 byte & The number of positions associated with the current item.\ & 1 byte & Parents ItemType type. \ & 1 byte & Padding.\ & 4 bytes & ID of expanded item.\ for each position & 4 bytes & The street segment itemID.\ & 2 bytes & The offset.\ & 2 bytes & Padding.\ & 4 bytes & The latitude part of the coordinate at requested offset.\ end each & 4 bytes & The longitude part of the coordinate at requested offset.\ {tabular}
